{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit\/UIView\/environment","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI","doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit","doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit\/UIView"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:17ViewEnvironmentUI0aB11PropagatingPAAE11environment0aB0AEVvp::SYNTHESIZED::c:objc(cs)UIView","extendedModule":"ViewEnvironmentUI","modules":[{"relatedModules":["ViewEnvironmentUI"],"name":"WorkflowUI"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","text":"ViewEnvironment"}],"title":"environment","symbolKind":"property"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"ViewEnvironment","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/workflowui\/uikit\/uiview\/environment"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/ViewEnvironment","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","text":"ViewEnvironment"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and provide those overrides in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customize(environment:)"},{"type":"text","text":". E.g.:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property gets the environment by recursively walking to the root of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation path, and applying customizations on the way back down. The invalidation path may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interrupted if a node has set it’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentAncestor"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", even if there is a node"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which specifies this node as an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentDescendant"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to update the return value of this variable and have those changes propagated through the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation hierarchy, conform to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setNeedsEnvironmentUpdate()"},{"type":"text","text":" and wait"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the system to call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"apply(context:)"},{"type":"text","text":" when appropriate (e.g. on the next layout pass for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclasses)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"text":" conformers ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"must"}]},{"text":" call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"applyEnvironmentIfNeeded()"},{"text":" in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"viewWillLayoutSubviews()"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"layoutSubviews()"},{"text":" respectively.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"important","name":"Important","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://WorkflowUI/documentation/WorkflowUI/UIKit/UIView/environment":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit\/UIView\/environment","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","text":"ViewEnvironment"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"type":"text","text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy."}],"url":"\/documentation\/workflowui\/uikit\/uiview\/environment","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"environment"},"doc://WorkflowUI/documentation/WorkflowUI":{"url":"\/documentation\/workflowui","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"type":"topic","title":"WorkflowUI"},"doc://WorkflowUI/documentation/WorkflowUI/ViewEnvironment":{"title":"ViewEnvironment","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/ViewEnvironment","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"ViewEnvironment acts as a container for values to flow down the view-side"},{"type